+ Choose Temporal\nTypes Correctly
++ DATE
+++ Calendar dates only
++++_ No time component
++++_ hire_date, birth_date
++ TIMESTAMP
+++ Timezone-aware
++++_ Normalizes to UTC internally
++++_ Applies session timezone on read
++++_ Cross-timezone events
-- TIMESTAMP_NTZ
--- No timezone conversion
----_ Stored as-is
----_ Local schedules & meetings
-- Selection Guide
---_ Date only → DATE
---_ Cross-timezone events → TIMESTAMP
---_ Time as entered → TIMESTAMP_NTZ
@endmindmap
